==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: confiscated
<hw>confiscated</hw> <pos>adj.</pos> <def>taken without permission or
consent, especially by or as if by a public authority; <as>as, the
<ex>confiscated</ex> liquor was poured down the drain; the customs
agents <ex>confiscated</ex> the banned fruits</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> appropriated, confiscate, seized, taken
over.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

